  "title": "[Entry-Level][Travel Opp] Marketing & Sales Representitive",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for a <strong>Marketing & Sales Representitive</strong> based in Singapore to join our FUN and VIBRANT team that will support you in your journey here — <strong>Shaping you to be a better version of yourself.</strong></p><h3>Why you should join:</h3><p>- Work in a young, fun and energetic team<br />- Comprehensive 1-1 on-the-job training and coaching.<br />- Opportunities for local and overseas travel incentives. (Even if you are <strong>NEW!</strong>)<br />- Clear career progression path to a Team Leader role and MORE.</p><h3>Job Requirements:</h3><p>- No prior work experience is required; training will be provided.</p><p>- Minimum qualification: GCE 'N', 'O', or 'A' Level, ITE, Diploma.</p><p>- Outgoing, confident, and comfortable speaking with people.</p><p>Whether you are looking for a part-time, fresh graduate, or full-time roles, you are ALL welcome :)</p><p><strong>ARE YOU​ A THRIVER? Apply now!</strong></p>",
